{"tid":116733,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有養中型/大型狗既你 屋企幾大？","createTime":"2017-02-11T15:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T20:55:19.000Z","uid":57803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"245419f68d78f238fc44ff34e244138142e04294","tid":116733,"uid":57803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"有意想領養狗 好多唐狗都好可愛 但我屋企（4/5百呎）似乎唔夠活動空間 有啲人話多啲帶去散步就得？ 你地養咩狗 屋企幾大 一日帶幾次行街？<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b342f6c42376ae4aff6a4738ff3029c980a3849","tid":116733,"uid":76907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"村屋700幾呎 養左一大狗一細狗 唔算大問題 一日放一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有個朋友住500呎都照養2隻大狗加一隻貓 都冇乜大問題 但係間屋係幾重狗味 養狗最緊要用心照顧 就算得300呎都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b44b76f0572283fa30b494f820b90e6213b250e","tid":116733,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"3000呎左右 村屋<br />\n一貓一狗無問題"},{"pid":"3636cc9b20fe3776dd1b9bdd4392c7a37cbddbb0","tid":116733,"uid":22740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T16:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/12/000339_fd59109db1a4be7c1aa2cbe45f57b05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F12%2F000339_fd59109db1a4be7c1aa2cbe45f57b05b.jpg&h=a9101420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1400呎村屋..其實屋大細都無所謂..狗狗同你一齊就已經好開心.."},{"pid":"7b7997a53ef8eef1de6b24400f210845616d0d87","tid":116733,"uid":57803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/uplo