:0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T21:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/12/000339_fd59109db1a4be7c1aa2cbe45f57b05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F12%2F000339_fd59109db1a4be7c1aa2cbe45f57b05b.jpg&h=a9101420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1400呎村屋..其實屋大細都無所謂..狗狗同你一齊就已經好開心..</blockquote><br />\n好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俯家七個月大啦..都係領養番黎架😊😊<br />\n一星期岀兩三次寵物樂園或者彭福..平時響屋企或者天台跑.."},{"pid":"e8ef590063d1b05a4bb058096c231f789221ac4c","tid":116733,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ycioq83s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fycioq83s&h=8f6fc760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n700呎加天台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed09b15c90a47bf67bfa4368621d14419c13c0b","tid":116733,"uid":57803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ycioq83s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fycioq83s&h=8f6fc760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n700呎加天台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生活態度既感覺 <br />\n連我自己都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22da71f6d12f07eee9d8efda3a7eaa08b6ee674","tid":116733,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>村屋700幾呎 養左一大狗一細狗 唔算大問題 一日放一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre